    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You focus on your training and pull out your true strength, entering a form of tranquility. Your pupils dilate and your movements become like running water. For the duration you gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>You gain advantage on all skill and ability checks regarding bukijutsu.</li><li>You increase your movement speed by an amount equal to your taijutsu ability modifier times 5.</li><li>You roll damage dice twice, taking the highest result.</li><li>You can cast ranged bukijutsu with the clash keyword, as a reaction.</li></ul><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above <br />C-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank, you cannot roll skill and ability checks regarding bukijutsu at disadvantage.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast at A-Rank, you instead double the movement speed bonus. If this jutsu is cast at S-Rank, you may cast a jutsu with the <em><strong>Finisher</strong></em> keyword as a Finisher without needing to set it up with a combo.</p>",
